  "instructions": [
    "Mix flour, salt, and sugar in a bowl until combined.",
    "Whisk oil and water together and pour into the dry mixture.",
    "Knead the dough until smooth and let it rest for 20 minutes.",
    "Roll the dough into a circle and cut into equal wedges.",
    "Place a cheese slice on each wedge and fold into a half-moon shape.",
    "Seal the edges by pressing with a fork or finger.",
    "Heat a nonstick skillet over medium heat and lightly brush with oil.",
    "Cook each kachori on both sides until golden and flaky, about 3 minutes per side."
